  "title": "Lead Generation Specialist (Part Time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Sales Caller Role Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Reach out to potential clients to introduce products or services and create sales opportunities</li>\n  <li>Assess leads and arrange appointments for the sales team</li>\n  <li>Update and maintain customer information within the CRM system</li>\n  <li>Follow up with leads to build relationships and drive sales conversions</li>\n  <li>Achieve or surpass company sales targets and KPIs</li>\n  <li>Deliver excellent customer service and address any inquiries or concerns from potential clients</li>\n  <li>Stay informed on product details and industry trends to present offerings effectively</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Previous experience in sales, telemarketing, or customer service is preferred</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and persuasive abilities</li>\n  <li>Capability to overcome objections and remain driven in a goal-oriented environment</li>\n  <li>Basic knowledge of CRM systems and the sales process</li>\n  <li>Excellent organizational skills with attention to detail</li>\n  <li>Ability to work both independently and within a team</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude and a focus on achieving goals</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Competitive salary with performance-based bonuses</li>\n  <li>Opportunities for career growth and skill enhancement</li>\n  <li>A supportive and energetic team environment</li>\n  <li>Ongoing training and development to improve sales expertise</li>\n  <li>Potential for flexible working hours or remote work options</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Location:</strong></p>\n<p>Lorong Chuan</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Pay: </strong></p>\n<p>$10 - 15/hr</p>",
